column6: "MARKED FOR DEATH!" pt. 5 (of 6) Mayday is forced into a battle against the mysterious foes that have already killed one cast member! With the body count on the rise, Spider-Girl is not pulling any punches!  32 PGS./ALL AGES...$2.99
